Source: https://github.com/posthog/posthog.com/blob/master/contents/docs/error-tracking/upload-source-maps/web.mdx

This is an example of a source map comment that should be present in your served JavaScript files after successful injection. It helps PostHog identify and associate the correct source map file for de-minification. Inspect your browser's developer tools to confirm its presence.

```javascript
